Parameter data in src/schema/parameters.json is transcribed from the official
Nord Electro 6 User Manual (v2.6x Edition J), Appendix II: MIDI Controller List
(https://www.nordkeyboards.com/downloads/downloads-nord-electro-6). CC numbers
and parameter names are factual data; the transcription is covered by the MIT
license above. See README.md for attribution details.

